 a reduction of physical movement (observable by others, not merely subjective feelings of restlessness or being slowed down).<br />\n<br />\n5. Fatigue or loss of energy nearly every day.<br />\n<br />\n6. Feelings of worthlessness or excessive or inappropriate guilt nearly every day.<br />\n<br />\n7. Diminished ability to think or concentrate, or indecisiveness, nearly every day.<br />\n<br />\n8. Recurrent thoughts of death, recurrent suicidal ideation without a specific plan, or a suicide attempt or a specific plan for committing suicide.<br />\n<br />\n有5個或以上, 一定要有 1  或 2, 就算係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30dc6ff670019012170b221b36fdfc3efe58ab9c","tid":2421764,"uid":29280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed9d1ef5943dc7dad7bbd9d6e1fc284c43091c3","tid":2421764,"uid":12814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf196bb9c77df812d83f899b77425d2315a8cfa","tid":2421764,"uid":29280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f5b8cc628e108ada395386d2a229c5e2b141333","tid":2421764,"uid":201478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"唔該曬"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T18:09:39.000Z","msg":"唔洗客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保重呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T18:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T18:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b42f0a212438f77e344c3434d11204d7cde3aeb","tid":2421764,"uid":201478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf196bb9c77df812d83f899b77425d2315a8cfa","tid":2421764,"uid":29280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f5b8cc628e108ada395386d2a229c5e2b141333","tid":2421764,"uid":201478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a7d4876b